c: 42
v: 20
t: "Whoever is willing (to gain) the tillage of Hereafter, We will give him increase in his tillage; and whoever is willing to (gain) the tillage of the present (life), (Literally: the lowly \"life\", i.e., the life of this world) We will bring him of it, and in no way will he have in the Hereafter any assignment"